{"tid":600270,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"騰訊35億入股《刺客教條》遊戲開發商Ubisoft　持5%權益","createTime":"2018-03-21T07:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T07:59:08.000Z","uid":141624,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"0e94cc6b026e3860d1ff7df70a38e1074b233227","tid":600270,"uid":141624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T07:17:07.000Z","msg":"法國遊戲開發商Ubisoft宣布，騰訊（0700）將入股公司，持5%股權，並與其達成戰略合作，騰訊將Ubisoft旗下幾款最成功的遊戲引入中國市場。<br />\n<br />\nUbisoft旗下開發的遊戲包括：《雷曼》（Rayman）、《刺客教條》系列（Assassin's Creed）、《看門狗》系列（Watch_Dogs）、《極地戰嚎》系列（Far Cry）等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nVivendi退出收購 引入騰訊<br />\n<br />\n法國媒體巨頭Vivendi一直有意控制Ubisoft，過去3年累計斥資7.94億元（歐元．下同）收購Ubisoft 的27.3%股權，成為其最大股東，並期望進一步掌控Ubisoft 。近日Ubisoft 作出反擊，回購Vivendi 所持有其27.3%股權，根據雙方協議，Vivendi 將以20億元出售所持Ubisoft 的股份，並在交易完成後5年內，Vivendi不得收購任何Ubisoft 股份。<br />\n<br />\n建基於上述協議，Ubisoft引入兩名長期投資者，分別是騰訊以3.69億元（約35億港元）收購其5,591,469股份，約佔其5%股權；加拿大的教師退休基金Ontario Teachers 以約2.5億元（約24億港元）持有3.4%的股權。而兩名投資者均協議不會入主Ubisoft 董事會，騰訊亦同意不會轉讓Ubisoft​股份，或增加投票權或股權。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/170348\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F170348&d=8RtZhivwEXyJ6g6JeIdj0QCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=dd1dd114\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/170348</a>"},{"pid":"5087a3bd92c36b7bfcbca3172b96137de31f26d4","tid":600270,"uid":3405,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T07:18:31.000Z","msg":"騰訊食撚屎啦"},{"pid":"fcb7b4d4075867be586af16a7fd580c0262d1cda","tid":600270,"uid":99805,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T07:22:35.000Z","msg":"祖先記憶改做金兵,元兵"},{"pid":"5cdf076502c75b9b66a7e6ec5b21cab4cb902c5f","tid":600270,"uid":99805,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"fcb7b4d4075867be586af16a7fd580c0262d1cda","tid":600270,"uid":99805,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T07:22:35.000Z","msg":"祖先記憶改做金兵,元兵"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T07:22:46.000Z","msg"